verse.lines:
{lang-eng}Afar through that gold vessel
God's glory shineth bright;
There'll be no need of sunshine,
For God will be the light.{/lang-eng}

{lang-eng}With Christ, the Stone most precious,
God's city shall be fair;
And He shall shine as jasper
In cloudless glory there.{/lang-eng}

{lang-eng}All in His new creation
God's glory there shall see;
The vessel for that shining
The Lamb's own Bride shall be.{/lang-eng}
